# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# MiniDungeon AI-tooling evidence fixture — .gitignore
# Public publish: commit the Unity fixture + source + docs + sanitized reports.
# Keep all transient/generated/machine-specific files and the raw evidence
# archive LOCAL-ONLY.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Unity generated folders ──
[Ll]ibrary/
[Tt]emp/
[Oo]bj/
[Bb]uild/
[Bb]uilds/
[Ll]ogs/
[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/
[Mm]emoryCaptures/
[Rr]ecordings/

# ── Unity / IDE solution & project files (generated; can contain local paths) ──
*.csproj
*.unityproj
*.sln
*.suo
*.user
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
.vs/
.vsconfig
.idea/
.gradle/

# ── Unity crash / system logs ──
sysinfo.txt
mono_crash.*
crashlytics-build.properties

# ── testplay-runner transient run data (local-only) ──
.testplay/
.testplay-shadow-*/
testplay-status.json

# ── Transient evidence runner artifacts (regenerated by tools/run_demo_*.py) ──
artifacts/

# ── Python tooling bytecode ──
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# ── Tool backups ──
*.bak
*.bak.meta

# ── macOS / external-drive noise ──
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db

# ── Raw local dogfooding archive (local-only; NOT committed to the public repo) ──
# Only the explanatory placeholder README is tracked; raw .testplay logs stay local.
Other_Projects_testplay/*
!Other_Projects_testplay/README.md
